# Title: Renamed Msdt.EXE Execution
# Author: pH-T (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2022-06-03
# Level: high
# Description: Detects the execution of a renamed "Msdt.exe" binary
# MITRE Tactic: Uncategorized
# Tags: attack.stealth, attack.t1036.003
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_renamed_msdt.yml
# False Positives:
#   - Unlikely

OriginalFileName="msdt.exe" NOT Image="*\\msdt.exe"